
  * USAGE =>
	netfromto -h
	netfromto -i enp2s0 -f 8080 -t 192.168.72.242 -o 8080
	netfromto -i enp2s0 -f 8080 -t 192.168.72.242 -o 8080 -Y
	netfromto -a DELETE -i enp2s0 -f 8080 -t 192.168.72.242 -o 8080

  * ABOUT =>
	Script forward network from port to ip:port.
	Use -a ADD or -a DELETE to add or remove rules.

